{
  "stem": "6016.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I remember now, and until today, I have a habit to part.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "When I am with my sister, or with anyone, I share, I cut in half.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Sharing.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, the French the French prisoner of war, no.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But there was over there one German.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I'm sure that he has seen it and he ignored it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So that was a help.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So it was-- I was lucky.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then I had a woman too, who, every day, she put in one place like a container with soup for me.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And one German woman gave me a toothbrush, which I could bring it in the camp and exchange for some soup.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "If I had another toothbrush, I would.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So as my recollection, as I remember Neusalz, the good things, that I could survive over there, with my sister.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Though my sister didn't have this kind of work.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "She had no opportunities to help herself.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So both together, we shared and we survived Neusalz.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, she worked next to me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I supplied her with, with the able, that she would be able to work the waltzes.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That it goes like a wooden waltz that I brought from the French prisoner to supply her.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So it was a good connection.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was lucky with that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Of course, this women, if she would, if she would be caught, she would be maybe punished.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But she tried to help us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She was very compassionate.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I wish if I would see her now, if I would know her name.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I am grateful to her, yeah.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The daily routine was getting up and to count us, [INAUDIBLE] on the place, and then to march to the work, because the factory was close by.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The barracks were close by to the factory.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
